Why don't eggs tell jokes? Because they'd crack each other up! But seriously, I once asked my sandwich if it wanted to hear a joke, but it said it was too stuffed to laugh. Then my salad chimed in, saying it was too green to find anything funny. So I turned to my soup, but it was too busy boiling over with laughter! Moral of the story: Food has a funny bone, but sometimes it's just too deliciously occupied to show it!